Package com.hiddenswitch.spellsource.common

Class GameState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hiddenswitch.spellsource.common.GameState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class GameState
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    The fields that correspond to a complete state of the game.

    Notably, this class contains Player objects, whose Behaviour fields are not strictly state. These can be safely serialized since behaviours generally do not contain any state.

    See Also:
